"{\"uid\": \"thelocal.fr-20240707-aires-idioms-and-olympic-travel-6-essential-articles-for-life-in-france\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Local Europe ABV\\u00e4stmannagatan 43113 25 StockholmSweden  This week's practical must-reads from The Local feature Paris's Olympic traffic lanes, the secrets of French motorway services, rules about overseas inheritance, whether you can do work at a caf\\u00e9 in France, turning a second home into your main residence, and a few must-know idioms  Throughout the Olympic and Paralympic Games periods, some 185km of roads around Paris will be reserved for event-related traffic - with some lanes closing to general traffic on July 15th.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Local\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Local\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Local\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Local\"}, {\"begin\": 116, \"end\": 121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997859822771, \"rank\": 2.140176773718793e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 162, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9991850998040529, \"rank\": 0.0004609922439960348, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 259, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8628304088848171, \"rank\": 0.15884938723516714, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 370, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic